       [1mgetmouselocation [4m[22m[--shell][0m
           Outputs the x, y, screen, and  window  id  of  the  mouse  cursor.  Screen
           numbers  will  be  nonzero if you have multiple monitors and are not using
           Xinerama.

           This command updates the window stack with the window  id  of  the  window
